{"tid":778503,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時候好想人生重頭黎過","createTime":"2018-08-13T17:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T07:46:30.000Z","uid":180734,"like":40,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1d9e44f8dc1ce49c852b159717ae20a862fa03","tid":778503,"uid":180734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:42:30.000Z","msg":"有時真係好想砍掉重練<br />\n<br />\n屋企本身環境唔錯<br />\n前幾年搬去公屋就成日放唔開 又會自卑<br />\n<br />\n返工又唔係好開心 <br />\n明明好努力 工作表現上司都認同<br />\n但硬係好似不被重視 事業一事無成<br />\n<br />\n拍幾次拖帶帽<br />\n近幾個月識咗個男仔 好快就好似男女朋友咁<br />\n但係唔知佢從來只係當我朋友<br />\n定係未ready拍拖<br />\n慢慢我開始諗佢當我係咩<br />\n<br />\n哩一刻覺得自己生存好無意義<br />\n但已經後無退路<br />\n我真係好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be59887cd8e99d2dabcede32d93d75fa8a87370","tid":778503,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"如果係無記憶下重來呢？"},{"pid":"2ad9dd4c4f20d1af576320c9ebac95c06899579c","tid":778503,"uid":180734,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3be59887cd8e99d2dabcede32d93d75fa8a87370","tid":778503,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"如果係無記憶下重來呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"係咪即係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a825bf08670f73ee6ac21a654cce0c46f00cee","tid":778503,"uid":179645,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"好想從來都無存在過"},{"pid":"ca5984ca234b92c9a09caa0c750543af739ab85b","tid":778503,"uid":161352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"珍<br />\n你明明知道點樣做到一個男女神 學霸 多fd子 運動叻 人生大贏家<br />\n但時間已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461a2b6051d1a6a1a63c911d046db0cc3747371f","tid":778503,"uid":2572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T18:11:09.000Z","msg":"你點肯定重新黎過一定好D"},{"pid":"433f598e8b984485879ae